---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Comprehensive Financial Planning - Fee-Only Fiduciary Advisors for Federal Employees"
  description="Full-service retirement planning for federal employees from CFP® and ChFEBC℠ advisors. Fee-only, fiduciary guidance integrating all your benefits into one cohesive strategy."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="service-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="eyebrow">Full-Service Planning</span>
      <h1 class="heading-xl">Comprehensive Financial Planning</h1>
      <p class="lead max-w-3xl">
        Your federal benefits are just one piece of a complex financial picture. 
        Our comprehensive planning integrates your pension, TSP, Social Security, 
        taxes, insurance, and investments into a cohesive strategy designed to 
        maximize your retirement security.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a href="/book-call" class="btn btn--primary btn--lg">Start Your Plan</a>
        <a href="/webinar" class="btn btn--ghost btn--lg">Free Workshop</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What's Included -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" data-animate="fade-in-up">
        <span class="eyebrow">What's Included</span>
        <h2 class="heading-lg">Complete Financial Planning Services</h2>
        <p class="lead max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          Comprehensive planning covers every aspect of your financial life, from 
          benefits optimization to investment management to estate planning.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <div class="feature-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><line x1="16" y1="2" x2="16" y2="6"/><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="10" x2="21" y2="10"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Federal Benefits Analysis</h3>
          <p>Complete analysis of your FERS pension, TSP, FEHB, FEGLI, and all other federal benefits. We calculate exact retirement eligibility dates, pension amounts, and optimization strategies.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <div class="feature-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Investment Management</h3>
          <p>Professional management of your TSP and outside accounts. We design and maintain an investment strategy aligned with your goals, risk tolerance, and time horizon, with regular rebalancing.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <div class="feature-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 000 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 010 7H6"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Retirement Income Planning</h3>
          <p>How much can you safely spend in retirement? We project your income from all sources, analyze withdrawal sequencing, and create a sustainable spending strategy.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <div class="feature-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v16a2 2 0 002 2h12a2 2 0 002-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Tax Strategy</h3>
          <p>Multi-year tax planning including Roth conversions, withdrawal sequencing, bracket management, and strategies to minimize your lifetime tax burden.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <div class="feature-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 12h-4l-3 9L9 3l-3 9H2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Healthcare Planning</h3>
          <p>FEHB plan selection, Medicare coordination, and projection of healthcare costs throughout retirement so there are no surprises.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <div class="feature-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 00-4-4H5a4 4 0 00-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 00-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 010 7.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Insurance Analysis</h3>
          <p>Review of life insurance, long-term care, and disability needs. We analyze FEGLI versus private alternatives and ensure you're properly protected without overpaying.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <div class="feature-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><path d="M12 8v8"/><path d="M8 12h8"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Estate Planning Coordination</h3>
          <p>Review of beneficiary designations, estate planning documents, and legacy goals. We coordinate with your estate attorney to ensure your wishes are documented.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="feature-card" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <div class="feature-card__icon">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3>Ongoing Quarterly Reviews</h3>
          <p>Regular check-ins to monitor progress, adjust strategies as needed, and address new questions or life changes. You're never left wondering what to do next.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Comprehensive -->
  <section class="section section--gray">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" data-animate="fade-in-up">
        <span class="eyebrow">The PlanWell Difference</span>
        <h2 class="heading-lg">Why Comprehensive Planning Matters</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="comparison-grid">
        <div class="comparison-card comparison-card--bad" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <h3>Piecemeal Approach</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Different advisors for benefits, investments, taxes</li>
            <li>Recommendations that conflict with each other</li>
            <li>Gaps in coverage and missed opportunities</li>
            <li>No one sees the complete picture</li>
            <li>You coordinate everything yourself</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="comparison-card comparison-card--good" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <h3>Comprehensive PlanWell Approach</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>One team managing all financial aspects</li>
            <li>Coordinated strategies that work together</li>
            <li>Nothing falls through the cracks</li>
            <li>Complete visibility into your finances</li>
            <li>We handle the complexity for you</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" data-animate="fade-in-up">
        <span class="eyebrow">How It Works</span>
        <h2 class="heading-lg">Your Planning Journey</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="process-timeline">
        <div class="process-step" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <div class="process-step__number">1</div>
          <div class="process-step__content">
            <h3>Discovery Meeting</h3>
            <p>We start with a thorough conversation about your goals, concerns, and current situation. This helps us understand what success looks like for you and your family.</p>
            <span class="process-step__time">60-90 minutes</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <div class="process-step__number">2</div>
          <div class="process-step__content">
            <h3>Data Gathering</h3>
            <p>You'll share documents including SF-50s, tax returns, investment statements, and insurance policies. Our secure client portal makes this process simple and organized.</p>
            <span class="process-step__time">1-2 weeks</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <div class="process-step__number">3</div>
          <div class="process-step__content">
            <h3>Analysis and Strategy Development</h3>
            <p>Our team analyzes every aspect of your financial life and develops comprehensive recommendations. We model multiple scenarios to find the optimal approach.</p>
            <span class="process-step__time">2-3 weeks</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <div class="process-step__number">4</div>
          <div class="process-step__content">
            <h3>Plan Presentation</h3>
            <p>We present your personalized financial plan, walk through all recommendations, answer questions, and agree on next steps for implementation.</p>
            <span class="process-step__time">90 minutes</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <div class="process-step__number">5</div>
          <div class="process-step__content">
            <h3>Implementation</h3>
            <p>We help you execute the plan, from adjusting TSP allocations to setting up accounts to coordinating with other professionals like your CPA or estate attorney.</p>
            <span class="process-step__time">Ongoing</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="process-step" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <div class="process-step__number">6</div>
          <div class="process-step__content">
            <h3>Quarterly Reviews</h3>
            <p>Regular meetings to review progress, rebalance investments, update projections, and adjust strategies as your situation or goals evolve.</p>
            <span class="process-step__time">Ongoing</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Choose Us -->
  <section class="section section--navy">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" data-animate="fade-in-up">
        <h2 class="heading-lg">Why Federal Employees Choose PlanWell</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="credentials-grid">
        <div class="credential-card" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <span class="credential-card__badge">CFP</span>
          <h3>Certified Financial Planner</h3>
          <p>Rigorous certification requiring education, examination, experience, and ethics commitment. Less than 30% of financial advisors hold this designation.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="credential-card" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <span class="credential-card__badge">ChFEBC</span>
          <h3>Chartered Federal Benefits Consultant</h3>
          <p>Specialized training in federal employee benefits including FERS, CSRS, TSP, FEHB, and FEGLI. We know the rules that govern your retirement.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="credential-card" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <span class="credential-card__badge">AIF</span>
          <h3>Accredited Investment Fiduciary</h3>
          <p>Training in fiduciary practices for investment management. We're held to the highest standard of care when managing your money.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="credential-card" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <span class="credential-card__badge">Fee-Only</span>
          <h3>100% Fee-Only</h3>
          <p>We don't sell insurance products or earn commissions. Our compensation comes directly from clients, eliminating conflicts of interest.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQs -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header" data-animate="fade-in-up">
        <span class="eyebrow">Common Questions</span>
        <h2 class="heading-lg">Financial Planning FAQs</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <summary class="faq-question">How much does comprehensive planning cost?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Our fees depend on the complexity of your situation and the services you need. Comprehensive planning clients typically pay a combination of an initial planning fee and ongoing investment management fees. We're fully transparent about costs during our initial consultation.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        
        <details class="faq-item" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <summary class="faq-question">Do I need comprehensive planning or just a one-time consultation?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>If you have a straightforward question or just need a benefits report before retirement, a one-time consultation may be sufficient. Comprehensive planning is best for those who want ongoing professional management of their investments and continuous guidance as their situation evolves.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        
        <details class="faq-item" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <summary class="faq-question">How is comprehensive planning different from your free workshop?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>The free workshop provides education about federal benefits that applies to all attendees. Comprehensive planning is personalized to your specific situation, includes investment management, and provides ongoing guidance rather than a single educational event.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        
        <details class="faq-item" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <summary class="faq-question">What is a fiduciary and why does it matter?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>A fiduciary is legally required to act in your best interest at all times. Many financial salespeople only need to recommend "suitable" products, even if better options exist. As fiduciaries, we must put your interests above our own, always.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        
        <details class="faq-item" data-animate="fade-in-up">
          <summary class="faq-question">Will you manage my TSP directly?</summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We provide allocation recommendations and guidance for your TSP, but you execute the changes since TSP doesn't allow third-party management. For outside accounts (IRAs, brokerage accounts), we can manage investments directly with your authorization.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section section--gold text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <div data-animate="fade-in-up">
        <h2 class="heading-lg">Ready for Financial Clarity?</h2>
        <p class="lead" style="max-width: 36rem; margin: 0 auto var(--space-8);">
          Stop piecing together financial advice from multiple sources. 
          Get one comprehensive plan that ties everything together.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/book-call" class="btn btn--navy btn--lg">Schedule Your Discovery Call</a>
          <a href="/webinar" class="btn btn--outline-navy btn--lg">Start with Free Workshop</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .service-hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, var(--color-navy-dark) 100%); color: var(--color-white); padding: var(--space-24) 0 var(--space-16); text-align: center; }
  .service-hero h1 { color: var(--color-white); margin-bottom: var(--space-4); }
  .service-hero .lead { color: var(--color-gray-300); margin: 0 auto var(--space-8); }
  .hero-ctas { display: flex; gap: var(--space-4); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .section-header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-12); }
  
  .features-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: var(--space-6); }
  .feature-card { background: var(--color-white); padding: var(--space-6); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200); transition: all var(--transition-base); }
  .feature-card:hover { border-color: var(--color-gold); box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg); transform: translateY(-4px); }
  .feature-card__icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; color: var(--color-gold); margin-bottom: var(--space-3); }
  .feature-card__icon svg { width: 100%; height: 100%; }
  .feature-card h3 { font-size: var(--text-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
  .feature-card p { color: var(--color-gray-600); font-size: var(--text-sm); line-height: 1.5; }
  
  .comparison-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--space-8); max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .comparison-card { padding: var(--space-8); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); }
  .comparison-card--bad { background: var(--color-white); border: 2px solid var(--color-gray-300); }
  .comparison-card--good { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-navy) 0%, var(--color-navy-light) 100%); color: var(--color-white); }
  .comparison-card h3 { margin-bottom: var(--space-4); }
  .comparison-card--good h3 { color: var(--color-gold); }
  .comparison-card ul { list-style: none; }
  .comparison-card li { padding: var(--space-2) 0; padding-left: var(--space-6); position: relative; font-size: var(--text-sm); }
  .comparison-card--bad li::before { content: 'x'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--color-gray-400); }
  .comparison-card--good li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--color-gold); }
  .comparison-card--bad li { color: var(--color-gray-600); }
  .comparison-card--good li { color: var(--color-gray-300); }
  
  .process-timeline { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .process-step { display: flex; gap: var(--space-6); margin-bottom: var(--space-6); position: relative; }
  .process-step:not(:last-child)::after { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 24px; top: 55px; bottom: -24px; width: 2px; background: var(--color-gray-200); }
  .process-step__number { width: 48px; height: 48px; flex-shrink: 0; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: var(--color-gold); color: var(--color-navy-dark); font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: var(--text-xl); font-weight: var(--font-bold); border-radius: var(--radius-full); position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .process-step__content h3 { margin-bottom: var(--space-1); font-size: var(--text-lg); }
  .process-step__content p { color: var(--color-gray-600); font-size: var(--text-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-1); }
  .process-step__time { font-size: var(--text-xs); color: var(--color-gold); font-weight: var(--font-medium); }
  
  .credentials-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: var(--space-6); }
  .credential-card { text-align: center; padding: var(--space-6); }
  .credential-card__badge { display: inline-block; background: var(--color-gold); color: var(--color-navy-dark); font-family: var(--font-heading); font-weight: var(--font-bold); padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-md); margin-bottom: var(--space-3); }
  .credential-card h3 { color: var(--color-white); font-size: var(--text-base); margin-bottom: var(--space-2); }
  .credential-card p { color: var(--color-gray-400); font-size: var(--text-sm); }
  
  .faq-list { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gray-200); }
  .faq-question { padding: var(--space-5) 0; font-weight: var(--font-semibold); cursor: pointer; list-style: none; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; color: var(--color-navy); }
  .faq-question::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  .faq-question::after { content: '+'; font-size: var(--text-xl); color: var(--color-gold); transition: transform var(--transition-fast); }
  details[open] .faq-question::after { transform: rotate(45deg); }
  .faq-answer { padding-bottom: var(--space-5); color: var(--color-gray-600); }
  
  .section--gold { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-gold) 0%, var(--color-gold-dark) 100%); color: var(--color-navy-dark); }
  .section--gold h2 { color: var(--color-navy-dark); }
  .cta-buttons { display: flex; gap: var(--space-4); justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .btn--navy { background: var(--color-navy); color: var(--color-white); }
  .btn--navy:hover { background: var(--color-navy-dark); }
  .btn--outline-navy { background: transparent; color: var(--color-navy); border: 2px solid var(--color-navy); }
  .btn--outline-navy:hover { background: var(--color-navy); color: var(--color-white); }
  
  @media (max-width: 1024px) { .features-grid, .credentials-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .features-grid, .credentials-grid, .comparison-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
